cards.rules_text:
When Mountaincleaver enters, create a 5/5 red Giant creature token with trample, then equip Mountaincleaver to it.
Whenever enchanted creature attacks, creatures with power 2 or less can't block this turn.
Equip {2}

When Whsipered Edge enters, draw two cards.
Equipped creature can't be blocked as long as you've spent five or more mana to cast spells this turn.
Equip {2}

When Rootwoven Blade enters, create two 1/1 green Elf Warrior creature tokens.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 for each creature you control.
Equip {5}

When Tithefang enters, exile the top card of your library. You may play it until the end of your next turn.
Equipped creature gets +2/+0.
Equip {1}

When Boughcleaver enters, look at the top five cards of your library. You may reveal a creature or land card from among them and put it into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in any order.
Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Equip {4}

When Realmsplitter enters, destroy target nonland permanent an opponent controls.
Equipped creature gets +2/+2.
Equip {3}

Whenever you put a counter on a creature you control, put a counter of that type on Blade of the Worthy.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 for each +1/+1 counter on Blade of the Worthy and gains all abilities of keyword counters on Blade of the Worthy.
Equip {2}
